OL,3,C'I miss the mum that was' - the
OL,4,Creality of caring for a loved one with
OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,FBristol women who have cared for their
OL,8,Floved ones with dementia share their
OL,9,Fstory with ITV News West Country.
OL,11,FPeople in Bristol who have cared for
OL,12,Ftheir loved ones with dementia have
OL,13,Fdescribed the emotional toll it has
OL,14,Ftaken on them and their families.
OL,16,FDementia is a condition that affects
OL,17,Fone in two people in the UK, - with
OL,18,Fnearly one million people across the
OL,19,Fcountry currently living with it.
