OL,3,C'I miss the mum that was' - the
OL,4,Creality of caring for a loved one with
OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,FAnnie Somerville's mother had the
OL,8,Fcondition for 10 years and she
OL,9,Fremembers her mum showing signs of
OL,10,F"aggression", in the early stages.
OL,12,F"My dad, he was quite unwell at the
OL,13,Ftime, she was horrible to him," Annie
OL,14,Ftold ITV News.
OL,16,F"One time she turned around to me with
OL,17,Fa look of hatred and said: 'You're a
OL,18,Fliar, you've always been a liar'.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/13
