OL,3,C'I miss the mum that was' - the
OL,4,Creality of caring for a loved one with
OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,F"I miss my mum terribly. I miss the
OL,8,Fmum that was," Annie said. "But I used
OL,9,Fto feel guilty because she'd have
OL,10,Flucid moments and say 'where am I? I
OL,11,Fdon't live here' and then she'd go off
OL,12,Fagain."
OL,14,F"You just think, this isn't living is
OL,15,Fit?"
OL,17,F"We made it as good as we could and
OL,18,Fshe never forgot our names, she never
OL,19,Fforgot us, which was lovely," Annie
OL,20,Fadded.
