OL,3,C'I miss the mum that was' - the
OL,4,Creality of caring for a loved one with
OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,FTrish Hamilton-West's husband Nick was
OL,8,Fdiagnosed with dementia ten years ago.
OL,10,FReflecting on the early moments of
OL,11,Frealising her husband had become
OL,12,Funwell, she said: "Often you have a
OL,13,Flittle cliff, you fall down a cliff.
OL,14,FThere's a sudden and abrupt change.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/13
