OL,3,C'I miss the mum that was' - the
OL,4,Creality of caring for a loved one with
OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,F"I was noticing it with driving. Nick
OL,8,Fwas having a lot more difficulty lane-
OL,9,Fdriving in Bristol, but as time went
OL,10,Fon he was showing signs of agitation
OL,11,Fand not always being sure where he
OL,12,Fwas, saying 'I want to go home', when
OL,13,Fhe was in the home we'd lived in for
OL,14,F30-odd years."
OL,16,F"He wasn't happy. He'd stopped being
OL,17,Fhappy at home because he was agitated
OL,18,Fand felt restricted.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/13
