OL,3,C'I miss the mum that was' - the
OL,4,Creality of caring for a loved one with
OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,FRehana Findlay's parents both lived
OL,8,Fwith dementia. She said she began
OL,9,Fnoticing changes in her mother's
OL,10,Fbehaviour around 10 years ago.
OL,12,F"Four years out of the 10 years I was
OL,13,Fmanaging my parents on my own.
OL,15,F"My father, he progressed very rapidly
OL,16,Fin the last three months of his life.
OL,17,FPrior to that he was showing mood
OL,18,Fswings and irritability.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/13
