OL,7,FOne Bristol charity hoping to make a
OL,8,Fdifference to the lives of people
OL,9,Fliving with dementia is the Bristol
OL,10,FDementia Action Alliance.
OL,12,FThe organisation was set up by Tony
OL,13,FHall after the death of his wife
OL,14,FBarbara, who died in 2022 after being
OL,15,Fdiagnosed with the condition.
